      <head>Scope and Contents of the Collection</head>
      <p>The



        <emph render="bold">Cyrus Townsend Brady Letters</emph> contains four pieces of correspondence including a letter from the mayor of New York City, John Purroy Mitchel, thanking Brady for serving on the committee for the "visit of the Missions".</p>
